data.description: Welcome to this exceptional 3-bedroom home tucked away in a peaceful cul-de-sac. Revel in the fully equipped kitchen boasting generous counter space & stylish white cabinets. Immerse yourself in the luminous interior featuring vaulted ceilings, beautiful flooring, an abundance of natural light, and fresh paint. The primary suite invites relaxation with a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom featuring double sinks. This home is enhanced with recent upgrades, including a professionally installed roofing system comprising beams, plywood, and shingles. A new water heater, French drain along the back side of the house and a new vapor shield has been installed in the crawl space. Step outside to the covered back patio, perfect for entertaining and hosting barbecues. With these recent upgrades, this property exemplifies both style and functionality. Act swiftly—this beautiful home, with its array of new features, is sure to be in high demand!
